notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:18.118Z",codex-root,Prefer one coherent graph over merging mutually stale bot branches.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:18.118Z",codex-root,"Major upgrades must be validated together because test,lint,type and runtime packages share peer constraints."
