close_reason: "Supported dependency modernization is merged, tested, and the stale bot backlog is reconciled."
body: "## Scope\\n\\nUpdate Toon, Commander, Undici, ws, YAML, ESLint stack, Node types, Vitest/coverage, tsx, TypeScript, and TypeScript ESLint where compatible with the supported Node runtime.\n\nCompatibility decision: TypeScript remains on 5.9.3 because typescript-eslint 8.64 declares TypeScript >=4.8.4 <6.1.0. @types/node remains on 22.20.1 to match the declared Node 22 runtime. Commander 15 and Undici 8 require Node 22.19+, so engines and contributor documentation now declare that floor."
